e7eec172  //   2-second AbortSignal.timeout. Success -> "OBSERVABILITY: ON - JSONL +
b364da27  //   Langfuse OTLP (Langfuse responded <status>)". Failure -> "OBSERVABILITY:
59d0ef31  //   JSONL-only (Langfuse unreachable at <url>)". The SDK itself keeps trying
